headline: NRG Energy Q2 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: NRG's Q2 earnings and revenues beat estimates, with higher year-over-year sales and strong shareholder returns despite rising costs.

headline: NiSource Q2 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates, Rise Y/Y
